name: Impaired Existence
description: BFA#2 My nephew Jaden was born with PBD which resulted in brittle bone syndrome, visual, and auditory difficulties. However against all odds he has made it to age 15 and is literally one in a billion. The initial sale and the following residual percentage will be divided as follows: 30% to PBD research, 30% to Jaden's home care and 40% to continue making art to raise awareness on Peroxisomal Disorders.
